Reasoning: 
1. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - The paper discusses security threats and proposes a system to detect attacks, which falls under the scope of this sub-category.
2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The proposed system utilizes Wi-Fi signals to detect attacks, which is related to networking and internet architecture.
3. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper mentions the correlation of live video feeds, which suggests the use of computer vision techniques.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with video feeds and their manipulation, which is related to multimedia.
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The proposed system involves the integration of different components to detect attacks, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
